headline: Why Walmart, D.R. Horton are this strategist's top stock picks
summary: Laffer Tengler Investments CEO and CIO Nancy Tengler explains why Walmart (WMT) and D.R. Horton (DHI) are still among her firm's top stock picks. headline: Why D.R. Horton (DHI) Stock Is Trading Up Today
